:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Encrypted Connection\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Security\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"SSL\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wplook.com/?p=15354\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:630:\"<p>What is HTTPS Encrypted Connection? HTTPS (Hypertext Transfer Protocol Secure) is a combination of two protocols, HTTP (Hypertext Transfer Protocol) and SSL / TLS. HTTP uses port 80 and HTTPS uses port 443,&#160;the second one has an encryption algorithm that ensures secure data transmission through an HTTPS encrypted connection.&#160;The &#8220;S&#8221; at the end of HTTPS [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/https-encrypted-connection-ssl/\">4 Reasons Why You Should Use an HTTPS Encrypted Connection</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Valeriu Tihai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7851:\"\n<h3>What is HTTPS Encrypted Connection?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/HTTPS-Encrypted-Connection-ssl.jpg\" alt=\"HTTPS Encrypted Connection - SSL\" class=\"wp-image-15446\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/HTTPS-Encrypted-Connection-ssl.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/HTTPS-Encrypted-Connection-ssl-600x318.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/HTTPS-Encrypted-Connection-ssl-300x159.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/HTTPS-Encrypted-Connection-ssl-768x406.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/HTTPS-Encrypted-Connection-ssl-1024x542.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/HTTPS-Encrypted-Connection-ssl-610x323.jpg 610w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>HTTPS (Hypertext Transfer Protocol Secure) is a combination of two protocols, HTTP (Hypertext Transfer Protocol) and SSL / TLS. HTTP uses port 80 and HTTPS uses port 443,&nbsp;the second one has an encryption algorithm that ensures secure data transmission through an HTTPS encrypted connection.&nbsp;The &#8220;S&#8221; at the end of HTTPS stands for &#8220;Secure&#8221;.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SSL / TLS uses two keys for this, the <strong>public key</strong> that is used when visitors interact with the site by sending different data (a comment, vote, transaction etc.) that are encrypted and transmitted to the server, the server receiving these data applies the <strong>private key</strong> to decrypt messages, the private key is only used by the server.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In other words, you encrypt messages on your computer with the public key (which is why you must have an updated browser) in order to be sent to the server that decrypts them with the private key.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>HTTPS protects you only while transmitting data between your computer and web server. If your private key has been stolen by a hacker then he will be able to decrypt your messages, so server security remains just as important to your site&#8217;s security.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why do I need an HTTPS encrypted connection?</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n	<li><strong>Security</strong> &#8211; When browsing the Internet and visiting sites that do not have valid HTTPS, your data is transmitted in an open format and anyone is able to intercept this data. WebSite visitors want to be protected, they do not want their data to be stolen;</li>\n	<li><strong>SEO</strong> &#8211; In 2014, Google mentioned it would increase the ranking (see: <a href=\"https://webmasters.googleblog.com/2014/08/https-as-ranking-signal.html\">HTTPS as a ranking signal</a> ) and will favor sites that use https as a search result, as everyone who wants to appear on the first page of search results have to use an Encrypted connection so this is the only change to  increase your chances;</li>\n	<li><strong>A Safer Web</strong> &#8211; Again Google, this time with Google Chrome, starting with version 56, when you fill in your password fields or card information it will show that this site is not safe; This will be just the beginning because in the future versions will be even more aggressive where the red warning triangle will appear in the address bar. </li>\n	<li><strong>Online Stores</strong> &#8211; The vast majority of plugins or modules dealing with online transactions will no longer work without https.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>How much does it cost?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;<strong>Let&#8217;s Encrypt</strong>&#8221; gives you free certificates, soon they will become one of the biggest players in the field.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Site administrators who have been notified by Google that the browser will alert users in January 2017, have rushed to pass the sites from http to https. You can&nbsp;see in the above graph a significant increase in November-December 2016.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Lets-Encrypt-Growth.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-15355\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Lets-Encrypt-Growth.png 940w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Lets-Encrypt-Growth-600x287.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Lets-Encrypt-Growth-300x144.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Lets-Encrypt-Growth-768x368.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Lets-Encrypt-Growth-610x292.png 610w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s Encrypt is supported by many large companies such as Google, Mozilla, Cisco, OVH, Facebook, Automattic, etc.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/index.php?rp=%2Fstore%2Fssl-certificates&amp;utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=not_secure&amp;utm_term=ssl_certificate\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Get Your SSL Certificate (Cheap)</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Certificates can be divided into three types:</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>DV Certificates</strong> &#8211; In this case, the Certification Authority checks (usually automatically online) if you own the domain name and get the green locker. The price range is 10-400 USD;</li><li><strong>OV Certificates</strong> &#8211; You need to demonstrate to the certifying authority that you are the legal entity that owns the domain, usually they request the info on paper, so it will take a bit until you get the certificate. The Price is between&nbsp;50-1000 USD;</li><li><strong>EV Certificates</strong> &#8211; To obtain this type of certificate, you need to submit a&nbsp;different kind of information that is checked manually like legal address, phone number, data about the individual/business, type of activity, etc., &nbsp;This gives your visitors a visual assurance of your security where the name of the company is indicated.&nbsp;It is perfect for online stores to increase buyer&#8217;s confidence, the conversion can usually increase up to 3%. The price &#8211; 190-1500 USD.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/https-Certificate-EV.jpg\" alt=\"https Encrypted Connection - SSL\" class=\"wp-image-15356\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/https-Certificate-EV.jpg 700w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/https-Certificate-EV-600x46.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/https-Certificate-EV-300x23.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/https-Certificate-EV-610x47.jpg 610w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So now you&#8217;re sure you have the question: What&#8217;s the difference between a free one and $1500 certificate besides the Green bar?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The answer is very simple: The Warranty! The higher the price, the greater the Warranty.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/index.php?rp=%2Fstore%2Fssl-certificates&amp;utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=not_secure&amp;utm_term=ssl_certificate\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Get Your SSL Certificate (Cheap)</a>\n\n\n\n<p>Note: If you have a certificate I suggest to be careful when it expires and extend it at least one week before the expiration date. If you forget to renew it the red bar will be displayed and will warn all visitors that the website is not secured!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Buy good certificates, generate public and private keys, install and configure the server to receive encrypted messages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wplook.com/contact-us/\">Contact us if you need any help!</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/https-encrypted-connection-ssl/\">4 Reasons Why You Should Use an HTTPS Encrypted Connection</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/0J3DL1AZCi0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://wplook.com/https-encrypted-connection-ssl/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://wplook.com/https-encrypted-connection-ssl/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"13+ Best Code Editors Available in 2018 [Updated]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wplook/~3/50QCgBEu2MM/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://wplook.com/13-best-code-editors-available-2018/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 07 Sep 2018 11:00:50 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Collections\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wplook.com/?p=17956\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:558:\"<p>A code editor is a place where a programmer spends most of his time and it is an essential part of every software developing. With such a significant number of programming text editors today, picking the best one for your day to day work becomes overwhelming.In this article, we want to present 13+ Best Code [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/13-best-code-editors-available-2018/\">13+ Best Code Editors Available in 2018 [Updated]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Diana\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23020:\"\n<p>A code editor is a place where a programmer spends most of his time and it is an essential part of every software developing. With such a significant number of programming text editors today, picking the best one for your day to day work becomes overwhelming.<br/>In this article, we want to present 13+ Best Code Editors that we consider are the best for editing and debugging code. We trust you will get enough information to make a decision that best fits your necessities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Please let us know what&#8217;s your favorite code editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Atom</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Screenshot-2018-01-08-13.20.56-1024x755.png\" alt=\"Atom code editor\" class=\"wp-image-17960\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Screenshot-2018-01-08-13.20.56-1024x755.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Screenshot-2018-01-08-13.20.56-600x443.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Screenshot-2018-01-08-13.20.56-300x221.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Screenshot-2018-01-08-13.20.56-768x566.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Atom is a multiplatform code editor (Windows, Linux, and Mac) that can be used for free and, a perfect tool for junior and advanced programmers. This code editor tool has all the features you could ask for in a code editor like a context autocomplete system, language autodetection, syntax highlighting, the possibility of using different panels and much more. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The text editor is very easy to customize, and you can search for and install new packages to get you started with your customizations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://atom.io?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=atom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Atom</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sublime Text</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Sublim-Text-code-editor.jpg\" alt=\"Sublime Text - Code Editor\" class=\"wp-image-17994\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Sublim-Text-code-editor.jpg 1920w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Sublim-Text-code-editor-600x383.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Sublim-Text-code-editor-300x191.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Sublim-Text-code-editor-768x490.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Sublim-Text-code-editor-1024x653.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Sublime Text is an incredibly fast, completely customizable, feature packed text and development editor available for Mac, Windows, and Linux. It is built from custom components, providing for unmatched responsiveness and comes with all the amazing features you would expect from a great code editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Powerful and simple is the best description of the Sublime Text tool. It can facilitate your continuous work activity of the day, you can find the information very quickly through many documents and edit it quickly. Sublime Text code editor uses a custom UI toolkit, optimized for speed and beauty while taking advantage of native functionality on each platform.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: $70</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.sublimetext.com?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=sublimetext\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Sublime Text</a>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/business/studio-8-agency-wordpress-theme/?utm_source=Article&amp;utm_medium=Link&amp;utm_campaign=Studio8&amp;utm_content=code-editors\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fbad2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-24272\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fbad2.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fbad2-300x157.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fbad2-768x402.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fbad2-1024x536.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/fbad2-600x314.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Visual Studio Code</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/visual-studio-code.jpg\" alt=\"Visual Studio Code- Code Editing\" class=\"wp-image-21894\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/visual-studio-code.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/visual-studio-code-300x178.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/visual-studio-code-768x456.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/visual-studio-code-1024x608.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/visual-studio-code-600x357.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Visual Studio Code- Code Editing</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another great source code editor recommended by our readers is Visual Studio Code, developed by Microsoft for Windows, Linux, and macOS﻿.  This is a powerful and popular choice among developers.  According to the 2017 Stack Overflow survey, 24% of web developers use this tool, putting it in the #5 position behind Sublime Text and Vim. VS Code provides comprehensive editing and debugging support, an extensibility model, and lightweight integration with existing tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Visual Studio Code permits changing the code page in which the active document is saved, the character that identifies line break, and the programming language of the active document. This tool is free and open-source, although the official download is under a proprietary license.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=visual_studio\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Visual Studio Code </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Notepad++</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/notepad-code-editor-1.png\" alt=\"Notepad ++code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18013\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/notepad-code-editor-1.png 767w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/notepad-code-editor-1-600x390.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/notepad-code-editor-1-300x195.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 767px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Notepad++ is a free and popular advanced text editor for Windows operating system. It is very versatile in looking at all types of files and it has many programming language syntax highlighters built in.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A great quality code editor like Notepad++ comes with a wide range of great and useful features and can be extended using plugins. It is a wonderful and simple option for beginners as well as for developers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://notepad-plus-plus.org?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=notepad++\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Notepad++ </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Coda</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/coda-code-editor-1024x653.jpg\" alt=\"Coda Code Editor\" class=\"wp-image-17997\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/coda-code-editor-1024x653.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/coda-code-editor-600x383.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/coda-code-editor-300x191.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/coda-code-editor-768x490.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Coda dates back to 2007 and in that year won the 2007 Apple Design Award for Best User Experience. This text editor only runs on Mac OS X and iOS and, it aimed to simplify the life of the Web developers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is a great looking, fast, and powerful tool with pixel-perfect preview and a built-in way to open and manage your local and remote files.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: $99</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://panic.com/coda/buy.html?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=coda\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Notepad++ </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>TextWrangler</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textwrangler-code-editor-1024x903.png\" alt=\"TextWrangler code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18007\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textwrangler-code-editor-1024x903.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textwrangler-code-editor-600x529.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textwrangler-code-editor-300x264.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textwrangler-code-editor-768x677.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>TextWrangler is a fantastic and powerful text editor for the Mac OS X system which came out of the BBEdit text editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is a perfect tool for programmers and system administrators as it is a powerful and richly-featured tool for composing, modifying, and transforming text stored in plain-text files. TextWrangler does an excellent job editing, searching, and transforming text and HTML code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: $49.99</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.barebones.com/store/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=textwrangler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about TextWrangler </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>TextMate</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textmate-code-editor-1024x635.png\" alt=\"textmate code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18002\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textmate-code-editor-1024x635.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textmate-code-editor-600x372.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textmate-code-editor-300x186.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textmate-code-editor-768x476.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/textmate-code-editor.png 1506w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>TextMate is a well-known code editor for developers who code on a Mac system. It has\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_24 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"24\" data-gr-id=\"24\">a</g> unique and innovative feature set which caused it to win an Apple Design Award for Best Mac OS X Developer Tool in August 2006.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The tool is excellent for development in modern programming languages and it contains a lot of great feature like search and\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_6 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"6\" data-gr-id=\"6\">replace</g> within the project, auto-indentation, column selection, word completion from the current document, dynamic outlines, etc, this is also the text editor that allows the building of Xcode projects within TextMate.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://macromates.com?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=text_mate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about TextMate </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Vim</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/vim-code-editor.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18003\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/vim-code-editor.png 1696w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/vim-code-editor-600x324.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/vim-code-editor-300x162.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/vim-code-editor-768x415.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/vim-code-editor-1024x553.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1696px) 100vw, 1696px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Vim is an open-source text editor designed for working with programming code in Unix and it is available for Mac, Windows, and Linux. It seeks to provide the power of the de-facto Unix editor &#8216;Vi&#8217;, with a more complete feature set.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has many features and the defaults are so well thought out that you really don&#8217;t have to change anything.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://vim.sourceforge.io?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=vim\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Vim </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>UltraEdit</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ultraedit-code-editor-1024x653.png\" alt=\"ultraedit code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18009\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ultraedit-code-editor-1024x653.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ultraedit-code-editor-600x382.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ultraedit-code-editor-300x191.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/ultraedit-code-editor-768x489.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>UltraEdit is a great text editor for Microsoft Windows, Linux and Mac OS created in 1994 by the founder of IDM Computer Solutions Inc., It will allow you to write and edit for HEX, HTML, PHP and\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_3 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_hide gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace replaceWithoutSep replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"3\" data-gr-id=\"3\">other programming languages</g>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>UltraEdit can help you modify, search, replace text easily and can also be used as code editor (several programming languages supported) with code syntax highlighting. The editor is simultaneously as simple and complex as you need it to be and is perfect to code and develop in different programming languages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The speed, flexibility, configuration options are wonderful.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: $99.95</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.ultraedit.com/catalog/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=ultraedit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about UltraEdit </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>BlueFish</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/bluefish-code-editor-1024x768.png\" alt=\"Bluefish code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18010\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/bluefish-code-editor.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/bluefish-code-editor-600x450.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/bluefish-code-editor-300x225.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/bluefish-code-editor-768x576.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>In case you&#8217;re a web designer  or a programmer who&#8217;s searching for a powerful code editor which is totally free, can be used in GNU/Linux, MS Windows and Mac OSX then, Bluefish text editor is surely one of the great!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has a variety of tools for programming in general and the development of dynamic websites. Some of the supported programming languages are C/C+ +, CSS, CFML, gettext PO, HTML, Java, JavaScript, JSP, Perl, PHP, Python, Ruby, Shell, SQL, and XML.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://bluefish.openoffice.nl/index.html?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=bluefish\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about BlueFish </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Brackets</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/brackets-1024x330.png\" alt=\"Brackets code editors\" class=\"wp-image-18123\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/brackets-1024x330.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/brackets-600x194.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/brackets-300x97.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/brackets-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Brackets is a modern open-source code editor designed for web designers and front-end developers that are working in HTML, CSS\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_3 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"3\" data-gr-id=\"3\">, </g>and JavaScript.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The interface of this code editor is very easy to navigate, and the extensions offer a variety of options. The Live Preview option is a really helpful tool\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_6 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-del replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"6\" data-gr-id=\"6\"></g> because you get instant feedback on any changes to your code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://brackets.io/index.html?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=brackets\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Brackets </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Dreamweaver</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/dreamweaver-code-editor.jpg\" alt=\"Dreamweaver code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18285\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/dreamweaver-code-editor.jpg 720w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/dreamweaver-code-editor-600x433.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/dreamweaver-code-editor-300x217.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Dreamweaver is a proprietary web development tool developed by Adobe Systems. This software has not only been designed with advanced level users in mind but also for beginners. It is\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_5 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"5\" data-gr-id=\"5\">an</g> easy to use program for new and intermediate developers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Dreamweaver you can easily manage, code and build complex websites using HTML, JavaScript\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_5 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"5\" data-gr-id=\"5\">, </g>and server-side programming languages.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: $19.99/mo</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.adobe.com/products/dreamweaver.html?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=dreamweaver\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Dreamweaver </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Aptana</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/aptana-code-editor.png\" alt=\"Aptana code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18286\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/aptana-code-editor.png 585w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/aptana-code-editor-300x196.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>With Aptana tool\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_12 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"12\" data-gr-id=\"12\">,</g> you can develop and test your web applications using a single environment. It offers web application development tools with support for a variety of programming languages, including HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Ruby, Rails, PHP, and Python.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aptana has great opportunities to modify the behavior of your IDE, that can include modification of themes to any kind of style you like and it has has a large amount of plugins and add-ons that you can install from the internet.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: Free</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"http://www.aptana.com/index.html?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=aptana\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Aptana </a>\n\n\n\n<h2>CoffeeCup HTML</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/CoffeeCup-code-editor-1024x458.png\" alt=\"CoffeeCup code editor\" class=\"wp-image-18012\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/CoffeeCup-code-editor-1024x458.png 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/CoffeeCup-code-editor-600x268.png 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/CoffeeCup-code-editor-300x134.png 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/CoffeeCup-code-editor-768x344.png 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/CoffeeCup-code-editor.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Regardless of whether you&#8217;re a familiar coder or simply beginner, you&#8217;ll like working with CoffeeCup HTML Editor.  It supports all major platforms including Windows and Mac and is a great and easy to use the tool when it comes to web development. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a good editor which highlights different types of HTML in color for easy visual referencing. Great for people who like to code HTML or who need to edit generated HTML.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Price</strong>: $<em>4</em>9</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.adobe.com/products/dreamweaver.html?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_code_editors&amp;utm_term=coffecup_html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about CoffeeCup HTML </a>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>The decision of a source code editor shouldn&#8217;t come softly. This is the place where programmers, web developers spend the most of their time and that’s why the code editor must be the best one!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We would love to know if you found your favorite code editor in the article or if you like another missing one.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/13-best-code-editors-available-2018/\">13+ Best Code Editors Available in 2018 [Updated]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/50QCgBEu2MM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://wplook.com/13-best-code-editors-available-2018/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"7\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://wplook.com/13-best-code-editors-available-2018/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s: