\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31004:\"\n<p>This post has narrowed down the list to present you 15 of the Best Gutenberg WordPress Themes right now. Gutenberg is a new content creator and editor coming soon to WordPress 5.0. It is an editor that uses blocks to create all types of content, replacing a half-dozen inconsistent ways of customizing WordPress, bringing it in line with modern coding standards, and aligning with open web initiatives. If you are planning on building a new website, we recommend you to choose a WordPress theme that’s compatible with WordPress 5.0 and Gutenberg. Here you will find the best Gutenberg WordPress themes you can buy in different kind of domains, just grab one and build your dream website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Makenzie</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg\" alt=\"Makenzie - Fashion &amp; Lifestyle Blog\" class=\"wp-image-22570\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-600x556.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Makenzie &#8211; Fashion &amp; Lifestyle Blog</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With features targeted to Lifestyle Blogs, Makenzie WordPress Theme offers many techniques that will ensure that your visitors read each and every post on your blog before leaving. The theme can be used for anyone wanting a unique and stylish design for a Magazine, Handmade Shop, Fashion, Lifestyle, Interior Design, Food or Craft Blog. Makenzie has a great SEO friendly code, meaning that Search Engine rankings and web traffic are taken care of.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The blog feature in this theme has a charismatic design that is sure to impress your readers. You can build an online shop using the popular and powerful WooCommerce plugin present in Makenzie. Other smart features include 5 Custom Widgets, 4 Widget Areas, MailChimp, WP Instagram Widget and Contact Form 7 integration.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/magazines/makenzie-lifestyle-blog-magazine-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Makenzie </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/createa-a-wordpress-site/?utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=get_theme_free\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get this theme for FREE\">Get this theme for FREE</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Benevolence</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/benevolence-church-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg\" alt=\"Gutenberg wordpress theme\" class=\"wp-image-23619\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/benevolence-church-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/benevolence-church-wordpress-theme-demo-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/benevolence-church-wordpress-theme-demo-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/benevolence-church-wordpress-theme-demo-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/benevolence-church-wordpress-theme-demo-600x556.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption>Benevolence &#8211; Nonprofit WordPress Theme</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The second from our list of WordPress themes compatible with Gutenberg is Benevolence. This is an eye-catching theme that is perfectly suited for Nonprofit and Church websites. The theme comes with many inbuilt options including 11 custom post types, multilingual options, an online store, and has a child theme included. This beautiful theme ensures that the website works perfectly and remains future-proof. When using Benevolence WordPress Theme, it is easy to incorporate galleries, sermons, donations and other church projects to the website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Benevolence is incorporated <g class=\"gr_ gr_16 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"16\" data-gr-id=\"16\">into</g> PayPal, making the acceptance of church donations easy. This amazing WordPress theme is the perfect choice for everyone looking to create a great website for church or any other non-profit organization.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p><a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/non-profit/benevolence-church-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Benevolence</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/createa-a-wordpress-site/?utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=get_theme_free\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get this theme for FREE\">Get this theme for FREE</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Charitas</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/charitas-charity-nonprofit-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg\" alt=\"Gutenberg wordpress themes\" class=\"wp-image-23620\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/charitas-charity-nonprofit-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/charitas-charity-nonprofit-wordpress-theme-demo-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/charitas-charity-nonprofit-wordpress-theme-demo-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/charitas-charity-nonprofit-wordpress-theme-demo-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/charitas-charity-nonprofit-wordpress-theme-demo-600x556.jpg 600w\" siz