data\";s:19872:\"\n<p>Blogging is a great thing that interfaces yourself with your interests, hobbies, personal life, food, fashion and much more. It is an amazing way to build your authority and showcase your knowledge on a particular topic. While choosing the best WordPress theme for your future blog it is essential that your blog looks great, professional, proficient and simple. Your blog must have a responsive web design that makes sure each visitor has a good experience at your site, regardless of the device they&#8217;re using.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bellow, you can find some amazing free WordPress Personal&nbsp;blog themes for blogging, portfolio, magazines, fashion&#8230; hope you can choose one and start your personal blog today!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover has-background-dim-90 has-pale-pink-background-color has-background-dim has-parallax\" style=\"background-image:url(https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/cropped-caleb-george-144977-unsplash.jpg)\"><p class=\"wp-block-cover-text\"><strong>Launch Your Professional</strong><br><strong>Personal Blog Today (for FREE)!</strong></p></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/createa-a-wordpress-site/?utm_source=post&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=get_theme_free\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Learn More\">Learn More</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. Morning Time Lite</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Morning-Time-1024x817.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18498\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Morning-Time-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Morning-Time-600x479.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Morning-Time-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Morning-Time-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Morning-Time.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Morning Time Free Personal Blog</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Morning Time Lite is a clean and simple Free WordPress theme with an awesome design, perfect for a Personal Blog, Family Blog, Journalists or anyone who loves to share their day by day thoughts in a very professional and interesting manner.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has <strong>great features</strong> that will help you to build the website you want:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Extremely Fast</li><li>Advanced Theme Options</li><li>Responsive Design</li><li>Clean Code</li><li>Multilingual Ready</li><li>Unlimited Color Schemes</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/free/morning-time-free-personal-blog-wordpress-theme/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_Free_Personal_Blog&amp;utm_term=morning_time_lite\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Free Download</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>2.&nbsp;BlogoLife</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blogolife-theme-1024x816.jpg\" alt=\"BlogoLife Simple and Free Personal Blog\" class=\"wp-image-18548\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blogolife-theme-1024x816.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blogolife-theme-600x478.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blogolife-theme-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blogolife-theme-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/blogolife-theme.jpg 1587w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> BlogoLife Simple and Free Personal Blog</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>BlogoLife is one of the best Free WordPress Blog themes for personal blogging. It supports post formats and several customization options. The custom background, custom header, and multiple color schemes give you the possibility to adapt your blog as you wish.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Responsive Design</li><li>WooCommerce Ready</li><li>Live Customizer</li><li>Testimonial</li><li>Plugin Support</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://stylishwp.com/product/wordpress-themes/blogolife/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_Free_Personal_Blog&amp;utm_term=Blogolife\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Free Download</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. Anissa</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Anissa-1024x817.jpg\" alt=\"Anissa Beautiful Feminine Theme\" class=\"wp-image-18501\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Anissa-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Anissa-600x479.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Anissa-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Anissa-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Anissa.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Anissa Beautiful Feminine Theme</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Anissa is a beautiful and feminine WordPress blogging theme available in free and premium version. The theme has been designed to look perfect on all size screens, and it is fully compatible and styled for WooCommerce, so you can use it to create your own online shop. It has a custom &#8220;about me&#8221; widget where you can add a photo and your social media links.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Responsive Design</li><li>Top Social Media Menu</li><li>Custom Header Image /Custom Logo Upload</li><li>Social Media Sharing Buttons</li><li>WooCommerce Support</li><li>SEO Optimized</li><li>Fast-Loading</li><li>much more</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://alienwp.com/themes/anissa/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_Free_Personal_Blog&amp;utm_term=Anissa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Free Download</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>4.&nbsp;Juliet</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/juliet-1024x783.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18505\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/juliet-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/juliet-600x459.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/juliet-300x229.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/juliet-768x587.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Juliet Minimal Blogging Theme</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Juliet is a free beautiful and feminine Free Personal WordPress theme specially created for fashion blogs, lifestyle and personal&nbsp;blogging. It has an eye-catching design that provides an assemblage of incredibility productive and functional theme features for personal sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The theme is easy to set up, simple to use and is WooCommerce integrated. &nbsp;You can customize it just the way you want and it looks very stylish and professional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>WooCommerce Integration</li><li>Fancy Scrollbar</li><li>Sticky Posts</li><li>Two Theme Styles/Skins</li><li>Responsive and Mobile Friendly</li><li>Front Page Banner</li><li>Front Page Featured Posts</li><li>Text or Image Logo Options</li><li>Multiple Blog Feed Displays, etc.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.lyrathemes.com/juliet/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_Free_Personal_Blog&amp;utm_term=Juliet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Free Download</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. Blog Way</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Blog-Way-free-personal-blog-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-18552\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Blog-Way-free-personal-blog-wordpress-theme.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Blog-Way-free-personal-blog-wordpress-theme-600x479.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Blog-Way-free-personal-blog-wordpress-theme-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Blog-Way-free-personal-blog-wordpress-theme-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Blog-Way-free-personal-blog-wordpress-theme-1024x817.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption> BlogWay Clean &amp; Elegant Theme</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Blog Way is a modern, clean and personal blog theme ideal for travel, blogging, and lifestyle. It comes with beautiful design, it is easy to setup and it has a great range of features. It supports Woo-commerce and can be used for perfect e-Commerce sites too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want a minimalistic blog that can be customized without the need to involve a developer, you should check this out. Blog Way has a Premium version which includes a few other widgets to the theme.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Theme options using customizer API</li><li>Demo content import in one click</li><li>Woo-commerce Ready</li><li>Unlimited Color options</li><li>Author Profile Widget</li><li>Social link settings</li><li>100% Responsive etc.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://promenadethemes.com/downloads/blog-way/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_Free_Personal_Blog&amp;utm_term=Blog_Way\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Free Download</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>6. <strong>ZBlack&nbsp;Lite</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-black-free-photographer-blogger-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"ZBlack Lite\" class=\"wp-image-18555\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-black-free-photographer-blogger-wordpress-theme.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-black-free-photographer-blogger-wordpress-theme-600x479.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-black-free-photographer-blogger-wordpress-theme-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-black-free-photographer-blogger-wordpress-theme-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/the-black-free-photographer-blogger-wordpress-theme-1024x817.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><figcaption> ZBlack Lite Photographer Theme</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to tell the story of your life, share your great moments and feelings, or to write about your personal journey then ZBlack Lite WordPress theme is what you are looking for. The theme is an elegant and simple WordPress blog theme, responsive and retina-ready, it is easily customizable and has a lot of great features.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Customizer Options</li><li>Color Accent</li><li>Logo Upload</li><li>Post, Page Settings</li><li>Social networking share buttons</li><li>Translation Ready</li><li>SEO Optimized</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://zthemes.net/themes/zblack-lite?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_Free_Personal_Blog&amp;utm_term=ZBlack_lite\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Free Download</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>7.&nbsp;Activello</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activello-1024x816.jpg\" alt=\"Activello Free Personal Blog\" class=\"wp-image-18528\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activello-1024x816.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activello-600x478.jpg 600w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activello-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/activello-768x612.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption> Activello Free Personal Blog</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Activello is a perfect, clean and simple WordPress blog theme specially created for lifestyle, fashion, food, travel, sports, etc. The theme is fully responsive and mobile friendly and it comes with several custom widgets and fullscreen slider to showcase your content with style.<br> Activello is integrated with WooCommerce that allows you to create a fully functional eCommerce website. This blog theme is also SEO friendly helping you to achieve the highest positions on Google.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Responsive &amp; Flat Design</li><li>Retina Ready</li><li>WordPress Customizer</li><li>Featured Slider</li><li>Infinite Scroll</li><li>Plugin Support</li><li>WooCommerce</li><li>Translation Ready, etc.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://colorlib.com/wp/themes/activello/?utm_source=wplook_com&amp;utm_medium=external_link&amp;utm_campaign=Best_Free_Personal_Blog&amp;utm_term=Activelo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Free Download</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" cla