comes an integral factor. Whether you are a food or fashion blogger, one of the Lifestyle Themes listed below is sure to meet your needs and help you share your ideas and personality in an attractive way. We have also included a few Feminine WordPress themes to help you start\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_5 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"5\" data-gr-id=\"5\">a</g> gorgeous blog that will appeal to your female audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Makenzie</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg\" alt=\"Makenzie - Fashion &amp; Lifestyle Blog\" class=\"wp-image-22570\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/makenzie-lifestyle-wordpress-theme-demo-600x556.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Makenzie &#8211; Fashion &amp; Lifestyle Blog</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The name Makenzie itself is sufficient to get the beautifulness with this new WordPress Theme from WPlook Themes. With features targeted to Lifestyle Blogs, this Dynamic, Extremely Lean and Influential Theme offers many techniques that will ensure that your visitors read each and every post on your blog before leaving. Makenzie can be used for anyone wanting a unique and stylish design for a Magazine, Handmade Shop, Fashion, Lifestyle, Interior Design, Food or Craft Blog. Makenzie has a great SEO friendly code, meaning that Search Engine rankings and web traffic are taken care of. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The blog feature in this theme has a charismatic design that is sure to impress your readers. You can build an online shop using the popular and powerful WooCommerce plugin present in Makenzie. Other smart features include 5 Custom Widgets, 4 Widget Areas, MailChimp, WP Instagram Widget and Contact Form 7 integration.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/magazines/makenzie-lifestyle-blog-magazine-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Makenzie </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=32&amp;customfield[8]=Makenzie&amp;billingcycle=triennially\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Host This Theme From $5.42/m\">Host This Theme From $5.42/m</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>My Journey</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/my-journey-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg\" alt=\"My Journey - Lifestyle WordPress Theme\" class=\"wp-image-23631\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/my-journey-wordpress-theme-demo.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/my-journey-wordpress-theme-demo-300x278.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/my-journey-wordpress-theme-demo-768x711.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/my-journey-wordpress-theme-demo-1024x948.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/my-journey-wordpress-theme-demo-600x556.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>My Journey &#8211; Lifestyle WordPress Theme</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>My Journey theme has all the useful features and customization options you need to build a great looking Fashion, Personal or Lifestyle blog. The multiple shortcodes in this straightforward theme will help you to breeze through the web development process. This theme is carefully designed with attention to detail. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The elegant design in My Journey WordPress Theme will highlight your content pleasantly to ensure that your readers have a distraction-free experience on your website. WPlook Styler in My Journey makes it easy to make changes on your site without writing CSS code yourself. Use the Blog Archive section to make your older posts accessible by date and year.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/magazines/my-journey-lifestyle-blog-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about My Journey </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=32&amp;customfield[8]=My Journey&amp;billingcycle=triennially\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Host This Theme From $5.42/m\">Host This Theme From $5.42/m</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Magazine</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/magazine.jpg\" alt=\"Magazine -Magazine - LifeStyle WordPress ThemeWordPress Theme for Photograph Bloggers.\" class=\"wp-image-20675\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/magazine.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/magazine-300x239.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/magazine-768x612.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/magazine-1024x817.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/magazine-600x479.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Magazine &#8211; LifeStyle WordPress Theme</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_10 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar only-ins doubleReplace replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"10\" data-gr-id=\"10\">Magazine</g> is one of the most versatile and modern WordPress Theme that is Unique, Sleek and Easy on the Eye. It is accurately and professionally designed and developed with cutting-edge web design technologies to let you showcase your posts stylishly and awesomely. The Magazine WordPress theme has practical features to offer you more power to create an authoritative blog that will stand out among others.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can be used by Lifestyle, Travel, Photograph, Magazine and any sort of online magazine. The 6 Homepage Magazine-Style Layouts in this theme will allow you to showcase multiple contents on the homepage to keep your readers engaged. Monetizing with Magazine is a comfortable experience thanks to its WooCommerce integration. Other smart features in this theme include 7 Widget Areas, Unlimited Color Schemes\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_8 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"8\" data-gr-id=\"8\">, </g>and Social Media Section.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/product/themes/magazines/magazine-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Magazine </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/host/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=32&amp;customfield[8]=Magazine&amp;billingcycle=triennially\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Host This Theme From $5.42/m\">Host This Theme From $5.42/m</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Noemi</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/noemi.jpg\" alt=\"Noemi - Lifestyle &amp; Fashion Blog\" class=\"wp-image-24157\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/noemi.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/noemi-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/noemi-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/noemi-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/noemi-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Noemi &#8211; Lifestyle &amp; Fashion Blog</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Noemi is a Beautiful, Engaging and Responsive Lifestyle WordPress Theme for Lifestyle Bloggers looking to cultivate an online presence and community. With 12+ Different Blog Layouts and 600+ Google Fonts, Noemi will be perfect for any kind of blog you care to mention – lifestyle, travel, fashion, personal or food. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can change any detail of your website thanks to the built-in live customizer. What’s more is that you don’t need any coding skills to customize Noemi as it is carefully developed using clean code.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/noemi-lifestyle-fashion-blog/16226028?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Noemi</a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Health Coach </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/health-and-coach.jpg\" alt=\"Health Coach Blog &amp; Lifestyle Magazine\" class=\"wp-image-24161\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/health-and-coach.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/health-and-coach-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/health-and-coach-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/health-and-coach-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/health-and-coach-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Health Coach Blog &amp; Lifestyle Magazine</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Health and Coach\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_31 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"31\" data-gr-id=\"31\">is</g> a Stylish, Creative and Premium Sports WordPress Theme specifically crafted for all kinds of Sportsmen, Athletes, Coaches, Trainers, Nutritionists, Lifestyle, Runners and Healthy Lifestyle Individuals. Based on the robust ThemeREX Framework, this theme contains everything you need to create a blog in the health, sports, and fitness niche. It allows you to Showcase Your Skills and Achievements, Provide Testimonials from Satisfied Clients, Showcase Your Portfolio, Mission\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_14 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-ins replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"14\" data-gr-id=\"14\">, </g>and Priorities.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Health and Coach features a Clean, Valid and Ultra-Responsive Structure to give your visitors a perfect reading experience across multiple hand-held devices. Health and Coach theme works perfectly with WooCommerce, so you can create an online store and promote or sell your products. This theme is also compatible with WPML, WPBakery Page Builder, Events Calendar and Essential Grid.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/health-coach-blog-lifestyle-magazine/19070706?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Health Coach </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Matilda</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mnathilda.jpg\" alt=\"Matilda | Lifestyle Minimal WordPress Blog Theme\" class=\"wp-image-24168\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mnathilda.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mnathilda-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mnathilda-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mnathilda-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/mnathilda-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Matilda | Lifestyle Minimal WordPress Blog Theme</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Matilda is a Posh yet Minimalist Lifestyle Theme with creative details that can be used for a variety of purposes from Travel Blogs, Personal Blogs, Portfolio Sites, Art Galleries, Lifestyle Blogs and Similar Projects. This theme has managed to cut down on unnecessary things, which makes it appear crisper. This theme ships with 32 valid HTML Files, Eye-Catching Typography Elements and Custom Color Schemes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Matilda WordPress theme features a mobile responsive design\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_5 gr-alert sel gr_gramm gr_replaced gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Punctuation only-del replaceWithoutSep\" id=\"5\" data-gr-id=\"5\"></g> and boasts a minimalist layout that ensures that your content gets the maximum focus. Matilda is fully responsive and compatible with popular WordPress Plugins like WooCommerce and Contact Form 7.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/matild-lifestyle-minimal-wordpress-blog-theme/20678213?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Matilda </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Lavander</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/lavander.jpg\" alt=\"Lavander - A Lifestyle Responsive WordPress Blog Theme\" class=\"wp-image-24176\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/lavander.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/lavander-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/lavander-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/lavander-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/lavander-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Lavander &#8211; A Lifestyle Responsive WordPress Blog Theme</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Lavander is a Multipurpose, Resourceful and Elegant Lifestyle WordPress Theme. This theme has immense versatility and flexibility and could be used for a wide range of purposes like Fashion or Lifestyle blogs. Lavander theme provides you with different layout options to choose from. All the options are fully customizable to ensure that you can easily fine-tune your site’s design as per your requirement. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The theme would be ideal for any blogger striving toward minimalism. Like other Lifestyle WordPress themes in this list, Lavander is fully responsive and extremely flexible with clean code.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/lavander-a-lifestyle-responsive-wordpress-blog-theme/20140677?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Lavander </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kloe</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/klow.jpg\" alt=\"Kloe - Fashion &amp; Lifestyle Multi-Purpose Theme\" class=\"wp-image-24182\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/klow.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/klow-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/klow-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/klow-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/klow-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Kloe &#8211; Fashion &amp; Lifestyle Multi-Purpose Theme</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_6 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"6\" data-gr-id=\"6\">Kloe</g> is a Stunning, Professionally Built and Powerful Fashion and Lifestyle WordPress theme perfect for Fashion, Lifestyle, Parenting, Food and other types of blogs. With a contemporary, uncluttered and aesthetically minimal design and several modern features,\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_7 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"7\" data-gr-id=\"7\">Kloe</g> is all you need for your fascinating blog. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the key features of this highly customizable theme include One-Click Demo Content Import, Custom Post Types, Multiple Header Types and Behaviors, Customizable Mega menu, Select Slider, Video background Sections and Smooth Scroll.\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_8 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace\" id=\"8\" data-gr-id=\"8\">Kloe</g> has a fully responsive design which makes it look stunning on all modern devices.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/kloe-fashion-lifestyle-multipurpose-theme/14518723?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Kloe </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Josephine</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/josephine.jpg\" alt=\"Josephine - WordPress Theme For Lifestyle Bloggers\" class=\"wp-image-24191\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/josephine.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/josephine-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/josephine-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/josephine-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/josephine-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Josephine &#8211; WordPress Theme For Lifestyle Bloggers</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Josephine is an ideal choice for virtually any lifestyle-related site integrated with popular social media networks through sharing buttons and original widgets. Coded with site performance in mind, Josephine offers you a one-click demo import option so you create your website quickly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Live Composer Page Builder in this theme gives you the chance to change the styling of all elements in your website without any limitations. While it might not be top of the list, Look could definitely be worth a second look.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/josephine-wordpress-theme-for-lifestyle-bloggers/11020235?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Josephine </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>CheerUp</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/miranda.jpg\" alt=\"CheerUp Blog / Magazine - WordPress Blog Theme\" class=\"wp-image-24196\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/miranda.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/miranda-300x220.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/miranda-768x562.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/miranda-1024x749.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/miranda-600x439.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>CheerUp Blog / Magazine &#8211; WordPress Blog Theme</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Just as its name puts it, CheerUp will improve your homepage and entice more visitors to your site. CheerUp is a Lifestyle WordPress theme with\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_8 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"8\" data-gr-id=\"8\">smart</g> designed options customized for all kinds of lifestyle blogs and online magazines. The 500+ Possible Layout Combinations, Modern Footer Styles, Unique Blog Headers and Beautiful Post Styles in this exceptionally smooth theme add a professional vibe to the technical and visual performance. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>CheerUp has a fully responsive design complete with HD Retina Graphics to look stunning across multiple devices. It supports many popular WP plugins like MailChimp, Contact Form 7 and WordPress SEO by Yoast.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/cheerup-blog-magazine-wordpress-blog-theme/16430770?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about CheerUp </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<h2>Himmelen</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image shadow\"><img src=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/himmelin.jpg\" alt=\"Lifestyle WordPress Themes\" class=\"wp-image-24202\" srcset=\"https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/himmelin.jpg 1200w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/himmelin-300x230.jpg 300w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/himmelin-768x588.jpg 768w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/himmelin-1024x783.jpg 1024w, https://wplook.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/himmelin-600x459.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" />\n	<figcaption>Himmelen &#8211; Personal WordPress Blog Theme</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Winding up our list is Himmelen &#8211; a Moderate, Flexible and Delightful Lifestyle WordPress Theme completely committed To Food, Fashion, Travel, News, Weddings and Inspiration Blogs. The One-Click Demo Import in Himmelen means that you can get your blog up and\n	<g class=\"gr_ gr_7 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear Grammar multiReplace\" id=\"7\" data-gr-id=\"7\">running</g> in a few minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p> Smart features in this unique theme include 650+ Google Fonts, 2 Featured Posts Slider layouts, 5 Blog Listing Layouts, Unlimited Color Schemes and a Dedicated Support Team via Ticket System. Built on Bootstrap 3, this Cross-Browser Compatible theme has an Advanced Himmelen Control Panel for easy theme configuration.</p>\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/himmelen-personal-wordpress-blog-theme/13041311?ref=WPlook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"button green-button\">Learn More about Himmelen </a>\n<a href=\"https://wplook.com/wordpress-hosting/\" class=\"button pink-button\" title=\"Get Hosting\">Get Hosting</a>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Final Thoughts</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Take advantage of the above-discussed Lifestyle WordPress Themes to jumpstart your lifestyle blog. If there is any good Lifestyle Theme with an eye-catching design and useful blog elements you feel like we have omitted from our solid list, please let us and other readers know in the comments section below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com/lifestyle-wordpress-themes/\">10+ Best  Lifestyle WordPress Themes</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wplook.com\">WPlook Themes</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wplook/~4/czNUqsMojTk\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://wplook.com/lifestyle-wordpress-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"https://wplook.com/lifestyle-wordpress-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a: