(239, 1, '2018-11-24 17:09:39', '2018-11-24 17:09:39', '<div id=\"pl-144\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-144-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;vertical_alignment&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;}\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-144-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h1>Our Chennai based Charitable Trust was founded in 2015 by a group of like-minded individuals who have called the area in and around Thirurvalluvar Nagar, Kodungaiyur, Chennai, home for decades.</h1>\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-144-0-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"0.5\" ><div id=\"panel-144-0-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>WHAT ARE WE DOING?</strong></h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We have come together and formed this trust with the mission of improving the lives of Children and Elderly in as many ways as we can. We seek to support the two most disadvantaged groups in society, Children and Elderly.</h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We also pledge to improve the environment by planting trees and educating people about the importance of keeping our surroundings clean.</h3>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-144-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\"  data-ratio=\"1\"  data-ratio-direction=\"right\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-144-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" ><div class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\">\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h1>We offer more than supplies – we offer hope.</h1>\n<h1>We use donor contributions to improve the lives of children today and help establish a promising future for them. We Plant a Better Tomorrow.</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h1>Education</h1>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h1>Food</h1>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h1>Clothing</h1>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h1>Planting of trees</h1>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-144-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}\" ><div id=\"pgc-144-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-144-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\" >[siteorigin_widget class=\"SiteOrigin_Widget_Headline_Widget\"]<input type=\"hidden\" value=\"{&quot;instance&quot;:{&quot;headline&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;OUR TEAM&quot;,&quot;destination_url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot