(251, 1, '2018-11-24 21:33:57', '2018-11-24 21:33:57', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">BALAVICA</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"<strong>Balavica</strong>\", a school for special children and also a unit of TNFCT, was established as social initiative to serve the children in need with all kinds of developmental disabilities such as ASD (autistic spectrum disorder), CP, MR, Down Syndrome.</p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-250 aligncenter\" src=\"http://tnfct.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/balavica-school-1-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The school was started in <strong>Jan 2018</strong> with a goal to provide quality education, structured training and therapy to the children in order to meet their individual needs and preparing them for a normal life.  Currently, the school has Nine full time children and Four full-time staffs to assist them.  Further, Balavica provides OPT and other trainings by experienced staff for the \"gifted\" kids depending on their requirement.</p>', 'Balavica', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '91-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-24 21:33:57', '2018-11-24 21:33:57', '', 91, 'http://tnfct.org/2018/11/24/91-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
